#
Welcome to my website! I'm Noam.

![My face](https://fbcdn-sphotos-d-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-prn1/539011_10151015662908172_901292996_n.jpg)

###
A little about me...

I'm senior at [Olin College](www.olin.edu) studying electrical and computer engineering (ECE). I'm really excited about software, design, and robotics. I have no idea what I'm going to do after graduation.
